 ∑_{n=0}^∞p^n \cos(nθ)=\frac{1−p\cos θ}{1−2p \cos θ+p^2} 
|p|<1
|p|<1
 ∑_{n=0}^∞p^n \cos(nθ)=\Re\left[ ∑_{n=0}^∞p^n \exp(inθ)\right] 
= \Re\left[ \frac 1{1-p\exp(i\theta)} \right]\\= \Re\left[ \frac {1-p\exp(-i\theta)}{(1+p\cos\theta)^2 + p^2\sin^2\theta} \right] \\ =\frac{1−p\cos θ}{1−2p \cos θ+p^2} 
